com.tsgrp.migration.target

Class AbstractMigrationTarget

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.target.AbstractMigrationTarget
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MigrationTarget
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MigrationTargetBatch, MigrationTargetComposite, MigrationTargetFileFolder, MigrationTargetLogTester, MigrationTargetNoSql, SimpleMigrationTarget

    public abstract class AbstractMigrationTarget
extends java.lang.Object
implements MigrationTarget
    Implementation of MigrationTarget that takes care of most implementation-independent functionality:
    • Injection of Event Listeners, Configuration, ResultLog and Connector.
    • Declaration of instance's Connection, populated at startup using the Connector (although a subclass could override this behavior).
    • Plumbing to fire events at appropriate times in the lifecycle.

    MigrationNode Attributes Read
